Dialogue: 5,0:00:02.85,0:00:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, who's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:04.10,0:00:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,His face is so pretty.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.52,0:00:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:06.65,0:00:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you moron. He's in a guy's uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:09.07,0:00:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen him around here before.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.15,0:00:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't go to our school, does he?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:12.40,0:00:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not our uniform. Unless, he's a...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.82,0:00:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A transfer student?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:18.41,0:00:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a new transfer student today?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:20.25,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, so I heard.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.12,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems a bit too sudden to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.58,0:00:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the teachers just never told us about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:27.79,0:00:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hear it's a guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that, but people are saying he's a real pretty boy!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about stealing the spotlight!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.26,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone, I know it's a bit sudden, but we have a new student joining us today.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:38.93,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in, Tsugumi-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.60,0:00:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:44.94,0:00:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pleased to make your acquaintance, everyone. I am Tsugumi Seishirou.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to my time here.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.44,0:00:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! He's so hot!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.61,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's like a model!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cute little face!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.66,0:00:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pick an open seat.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.95,0:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.08,0:01:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Did he just snicker at me?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:12.59,0:01:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.92,0:01:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.84,0:01:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.93,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey wait! What are you doing?! Are you crazy? Everybody's watching!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.06,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mistress! I've waited so long for this moment.
