Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.48,0:01:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for my abrupt appearance.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.11,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Claude-sama has ordered that I guard you while broadening my own knowledge.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.61,0:01:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair enough, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:39.41,0:01:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, what's with your uniform?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:42.16,0:01:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:43.66,0:01:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As much as I tried, I was unable to acquire a uniform for this school. This was all I had.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.04,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly though, I wonder why he's dressed like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.79,0:01:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear him? He couldn't get the right uniform.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see! So that's how it is!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he couldn't! Oh well!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? You're creeping me out.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:04.93,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.98,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you picked up quite a handsome boyfriend for yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.02,0:02:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I must request that you introduce me to him, if you would.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.15,0:02:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right, yeah. H-Hey, you over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.41,0:02:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy! He's my new boyfriend!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.79,0:02:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard so much about you!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.21,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But to see you in person now, I can be certain that you truly are as reliable as they say.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clear now that the Bee Hive gang is in good hands.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.88,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this? I imagined a gangster like him would be nothing but bad news.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But he seems to be a pretty friendly guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.97,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me introduce myself more personally.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.19,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsugumi Seishirou.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Mistress and I are so close in age,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.11,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we often played with each other as children, essentially growing up together.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately though, we haven't had any opportunity to see each other.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.24,0:03:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I've been worrying \Nabout her quite frequently.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.37,0:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This gorilla woman?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.37,0:03:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gorilla?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. He's just joking around!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.83,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait a minute, she told me she's never had any friends or boyfriends,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.88,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but there's one right here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:16.67,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He counts, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:20.22,0:03:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, open wide and say, "Ah!"
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.30,0:03:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough! I told you, you don't need to feed me!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no harm in it, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when we used to eat like this all the time.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were just kids back then!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I watching?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.27,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't keep acting like this, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep it up?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.48,0:03:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! It's your favorite, Assam tea!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, enough already!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.58,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, you've grown up to be more magnificent than ever before.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh hey, doing all right there, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.62,0:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice-looking rival you've got over there.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you need to cut it out!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.46,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being so clingy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Don't you think that's a bit harsh, Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.76,0:04:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And to think there was a time when we would even bathe together!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.22,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's it! I'm going to the bathroom for a minute!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare follow me!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:07.43,0:04:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou-san.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.64,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you mind if we spoke in private for a moment?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to talk on the roof?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.57,0:04:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there is one thing that I would like you to clear up for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.99,0:04:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It concerns our Mistress. Do you truly love her with all your heart?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight I do!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was close! I almost denied it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.71,0:04:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How much do you love her?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I love her more than words can describe, of course!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you bet!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you go so far as to give your life for my Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'd give my life in a heartbeat!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see. That puts my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, would you die for her right now?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no! Hold on a...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.10,0:04:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What have I gotten myself into?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.99,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How disappointing.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Mistress had fallen for you,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but meeting you in person makes it clear that your attention span is that of a flea.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're far too slow, and even completely defenseless.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you expect to protect Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.67,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You have made it clear.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right to think that you have deceived Mistress,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.38,0:05:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and that she is bound by spurious love!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out! What's your goal here?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want our turf?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you plan to take over our whole organization?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Th-This guy...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I take back everything!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.18,0:05:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy's more bad news than I thought!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would Mistress fall for someone like you?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if she'd been deceived,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's not a single thing she would find attractive in you!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're spineless!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.90,0:05:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Insignificant!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.57,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And seriously, there's no way you \Ncould ever love her more than I do!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, what's he going on about now?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For a worthless gnat like you,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I needn't concern myself with \Nwhatever schemes you may have.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do this fair and square.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will release my Mistress from your evil grasp.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll see soon enough...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.63,0:06:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,which of us is more suited to remain by Mistress's side!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, that's exactly what I want.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.76,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not as though I enjoy being with her anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, no. Actually...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Losing her'd be a disaster!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.77,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kirisaki and I'd both have hell to pay if that happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.02,0:06:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you {\i1}were{\i0} fooling her, you punk!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This means war!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you run off yet!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got some nerve talking to me like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.36,0:06:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna know which one of us she belongs with?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us are truly in love! I'd never let anyone take her from me!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What's happening out there?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, wait. I sort of see what's going on.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.75,0:06:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! I just said something \Nincredibly embarrassing without thinking!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.30,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"In love," you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.10,0:06:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you're the one she belongs with, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.73,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Would the two of you stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on guys, what kind of silliness is this?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.61,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi! Darling!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have to get along, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, please stay out of our way.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.74,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect, Mistress, I cannot...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,accept that this man is your partner!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:20.25,0:07:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, do you remember?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The promise we made ten years ago?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise? Ten years ago?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After that day, I decided to become stronger
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.39,0:07:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to be able to protect you with my own hands.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All these years, I've been subjecting \Nmyself to a rigorous training regimen,
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.39,0:07:42.98,Sign #2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\b1\fsp-2\fs36\fax-0.4\c&H82D3FB&\frz353\fscx80\pos(322,379)}M{*\frz352.625\fax-0.375}e{*\frz352.25\fax-0.35}m{*\frz351.875\fax-0.325}o{*\frz351.5\fax-0.3}r{*\frz351.125\fax-0.275}i{*\frz350.75\fax-0.25}e{*\frz350.375\fax-0.225}s{\frz350\fax-0.2}
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.39,0:07:42.98,Sign #2,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\b1\fsp-2\fs36\c&H82D3FB&\fscx80\frz338\fax0\pos(468,427)}f{*\frz337\fax0.023}l{*\frz336\fax0.046}o{*\frz335\fax0.069}o{*\frz334\fax0.092}d{*\frz333\fax0.115}i{*\frz332\fax0.138}n{*\frz331\fax0.162}g {*\frz329\fax0.208}b{*\frz328\fax0.231}a{*\frz327\fax0.254}c{*\frz326\fax0.277}k{\frz325\fax0.3}
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.39,0:07:42.98,Sign #2,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\b1\fsp-2\fs36\fax-0.4\c&H82D3FB&\frz353\fscx80\pos(322,379)}M{*\frz352.625\fax-0.375}e{*\frz352.25\fax-0.35}m{*\frz351.875\fax-0.325}o{*\frz351.5\fax-0.3}r{*\frz351.125\fax-0.275}i{*\frz350.75\fax-0.25}e{*\frz350.375\fax-0.225}s{\frz350\fax-0.2}
