Dialogue: 5,0:07:37.77,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,honing my skills to become \Nmore powerful for your sake!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I pushed myself until I shed blood!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.31,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But all for what?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the man who is meant to be protecting you
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,such a spineless, flimsy, pathetic bean sprout?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot allow this!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mistress is the heiress to the \Nmagnificent Bee Hive organization!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think that you have what it takes to protect her,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll need to prove it before I'll acknowledge you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichijou Raku!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.54,0:08:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll battle for Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.29,0:08:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I challenge you to a duel!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.71,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you prove you have what it takes to defeat me, then I will acknowledge you as worthy of her.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:14.76,0:08:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if it is {\i1}I{\i0} who defeats you,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I will show you horrors worse than hell, and then... I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, hold on a moment! Can we just talk this over?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right, Tsugumi. You need to chill out a bit.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:28.61,0:08:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,After school, on the schoolyard.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.90,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be there, or I'll come kill you.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:36.16,0:08:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for Pete's sake!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping things wouldn't turn out like this!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you knew Tsugumi was going to do this?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I knew! Wasn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:44.00,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was Claude who set all this up.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi was adopted by Claude as a child...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and was put through specialized training and placed into elite classes for prodigies,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,all to become a top-class hitman.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitman?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, a few years ago some thugs tried to hit on me,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and Tsugumi tore them {\i1}and{\i0} their whole organization to shreds! That's how talented this kid is!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.48,0:09:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Singlehandedly, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole organization, you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:05.85,0:09:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I never heard anything about this!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.11,0:09:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there some way explain the situation, so that Tsugumi'll back off?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:12.90,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Tsugumi gets going, it's too late.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.28,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suggest we do then?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole city will go to hell if I lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not my fault!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who went and pissed Tsugumi off!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You reap what you sow!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.33,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a moron!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That guy, though...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He wanted to protect Kirisaki,
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.84,0:09:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so he stuck with his training \Nto become stronger.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.30,0:09:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For ten years, even.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's not as though Kirisaki dislikes him.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.72,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe deep down inside, Kirisaki wants him to win.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better not lose.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.81,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not like I care about what happens to you or anything, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.36,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll probably be a disaster for everyone if this doesn't work out.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:54.74,0:09:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot at stake here, so I won't forgive you if you mess this up.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you are so not cute...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,at all, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.33,0:10:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:06.16,0:10:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.54,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, I guess I have to do this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Might as well muster up some fighting spirit, I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:22.76,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I commend you for actually showing your face.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.56,0:10:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, this is my chance to show my honey how courageous I can be!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But that aside, can I ask you something first?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.11,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh! Tsugumi-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd this crowd come from?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.44,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.11,0:10:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All right everybody, place your bets!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One meal ticket per wager! We're running out of time!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put three on Tsugumi-kun!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.29,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm throwing down ten!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.33,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our duel begins the moment this coin hits the ground.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.04,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too late to back down now.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first fistfight I've ever been in, but still...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll give it my best shot
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if I'll even get to use my fists!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are those real?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What an idiot! He expected Tsugumi to fight unarmed!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.11,0:11:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't lose, bean sprout.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.86,0:11:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you running? Face me like a man!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.37,0:11:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to die! I'm really going to die!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't stand a chance in a fight like this!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.58,0:11:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your manhood?!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As I suspected, there's no way you could ever protect Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Only I can protect her!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:35.63,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get over yourself! All you do is go on about "protecting" her!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:39.42,0:11:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the one who doesn't know a thing about her?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.72,0:11:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't at all the type to just sit and watch while someone else protects her!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one lacking in manhood!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.69,0:11:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You call yourself a man? Then you should be there to watch over her!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.90,0:12:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you question my manhood! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all you're mad about?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,God damn you! I hate you more every time you speak! How dare you...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...speak as though you know me.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.08,0:12:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, I can't get anywhere with him!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just have to take my chances!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never escape me!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to cool off a bit!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.72,0:12:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,They just jumped into the pool from the third floor!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:31.31,0:12:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they okay?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.14,0:12:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.94,0:12:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe that actually worked.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was so scary! I thought I was about to die!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This is hopeless. He's out like a light.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.87,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But now what am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When he wakes up, it'll be the same thing all over again.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.21,0:13:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But first things first. I'm gonna catch a cold if I don't get changed soon.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jeez. I'd feel bad just leaving him out if he caught a cold.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.43,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a drag. Why do I have to undress another dude?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You villain! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.24,0:13:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now, I was just...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-A girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:38.00,0:13:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But he wears a guy's uniform!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And his name is Seishirou!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Raku!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap! There's people!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This can't end well.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If people see you like this...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, quick! Clothes! Your clothes!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.64,0:13:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from me, you fiend!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I could have sworn I heard people in here.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could he have gone?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:07.15,0:14:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We've looked everywhere in here now, haven't we?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I had no choice,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:14.79,0:14:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,not with everyone just outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.29,0:14:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand that,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but why do I have to be stuck here with you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! I'm seriously sorry!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirisaki-san! There's no one in the girls' locker room, either!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:27.34,0:14:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But why did you want us to check in there, anyway?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.85,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else? Because Tsugumi's a girl, of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.56,0:14:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.06,0:14:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really are a girl?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.60,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I was a boy too?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.77,0:14:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never understood why, but people have continuously mistook me for a boy my entire life.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:48.20,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For goodness sake, I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.91,0:14:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hold up! You wear a guy's uniform! Why?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.45,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier to move around in, why else?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wore something as frilly as that girls' uniform,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd hinder my reaction time.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:01.42,0:15:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'm sorry, but if I'd known you were a girl, this would never have happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.88,0:15:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want Mistress to see me in such a shameful condition anyway.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:15.43,0:15:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pathetic. I can't believe \NI lost to the likes of you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I think that I could protect Mistress?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How will I ever show my face to Mistress again, after being reduced to such a state?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, this girl...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Talk about a 180-degree turn!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.53,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, she's a {\i0}girl{\i1}.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.28,0:15:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This situation could be pretty dangerous!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so dark in here, and we're so close that I can hear her breathing.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.91,0:15:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels like something soft is \Npressing against my body too.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.66,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, if I really look, her curves are actually pretty feminine!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.21,0:15:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's getting me all flustered now! I need to calm down!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:48.71,0:15:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know! I'll just think about Onodera.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.34,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Onodera, Ono...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, Raku!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey wait, your name... Seishirou.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that an alias?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How rude! It's my real name!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.23,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I was abandoned at birth, you see.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who adopted me gave me that name.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.95,0:16:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, he thought that I was a boy.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.91,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Consulting a name dictionary, he picked one completely at random for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Seishirou!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.45,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Four Eyes...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.66,0:16:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, as unbelievable as it sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.31,0:16:29.32,LeviUnbrushed - Copy - Copy - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB46D70&\blur0.5\fs32\frz10\pos(675,127)}Why are you \Nbeing so shy{\1c&H564BBE&}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.32,LeviUnbrushed - Copy - Copy - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\an1\fs32\blur0.5\c&H4B3DC0&\pos(287,551)}Are you \Na moron{\c&H559BD0&}!?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.33,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,even after raising me for ten years, he still doesn't realize that I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.50,0:16:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:29.30,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that it makes a difference to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to fulfill my mission to protect Mistress,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:35.64,0:16:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long since given up on being a girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.51,0:16:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:40.72,0:16:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I gave up on being a girl,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:43.35,0:16:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and became strong enough to confidently face any man. But I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.48,0:16:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't protect Mistress, then what am I good for?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:52.53,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, that's a shame, \Nbecause you're actually pretty cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.03,0:16:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous! How can you say that I'm cute?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's ever said that to me...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,until today.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What in God's name do you think you're doing, you pig insect?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:20.76,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:23.35,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You also thought that Tsugumi was a boy, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.40,0:17:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.23,0:17:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,how did your duel turn out?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.15,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand this, Ichijou Raku!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.03,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't lost to you just yet, you got that?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:40.95,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:42.29,0:17:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You still haven't proved that you have what it takes to protect my Mistress,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.58,0:17:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and that was the whole point of the duel!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:48.17,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So that outcome's invalid!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll worry about how to deal with you later,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.75,0:17:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I determine that you're not good enough for her, you'll be staring down a barrel again!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So keep that in mind and give her your best!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:57.76,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right? Whatever you say.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Raku!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouko-chan said you have to put in a letter of apology,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.18,0:18:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for using the pool without permission.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, honey, I'll be back in a minute.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:08.31,0:18:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, he completely defeated me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He said something to me.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:20.37,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that you're not the type to just sit and watch while somebody else protected you.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:25.12,0:18:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He said that?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with everybody worrying about you,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.04,0:18:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you've always been able to take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You also were always the kid who'd come home with a big smile covered in dirt.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.88,0:18:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Trusting in you as I watch over you...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different type of strength, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.43,0:18:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know, I still wonder why everyone seems to mistake me for a guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.27,0:18:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder that myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.57,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey, Mistress...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.37,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the point of this again?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you making me wear this?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! I knew that'd look good on you!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.38,0:19:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You look so adorable, Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I am most certainly {\i1}not{\i0} cute!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.51,0:19:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go again.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a girl, Tsugumi, so you gotta dress like one!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.10,0:19:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need for that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.56,0:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to protect you,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.35,0:19:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and to fulfill the promise we made together!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:32.10,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Tsugumi! Remind me what that promise was about?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard I tried, I couldn't remember it at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:39.49,0:19:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I thought you might have forgotten about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:43.57,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.53,0:19:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the day that we met, became friends,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.20,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and bathed together for the first time.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I said...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, I'll become the kind of person who can protect you, Mistress!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.34,0:19:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good luck!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's even more off-hand than I imagined!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:02.51,0:20:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? You've been living for a promise like that this whole time?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.18,0:20:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a very important \Nmoment for me, you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to be honest, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.06,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But can you blame me for not remembering?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.40,0:20:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's amazing that you could remember something from that long ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress, you
Dialogue: 5,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.28,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi, this is for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.32,0:20:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, nobody could mistake you for a boy, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:28.24,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mistress, I'm truly grateful for your kindness,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but something this feminine could never suit me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.17,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's with the ribbon?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks great on you! It's cute.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No it's not!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:54.77,0:20:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, Mistress just now...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.48,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me, the promise she made ten years ago with her first love...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Has she forgotten that as well?
